  <brief_title>Rituximab in Metastatic Melanoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Rituximab, an Anti-CD20 (Cluster of Differentiation Antigen 20) Therapeutic Agent, in Metastatic Melanoma: a Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
