  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether rituximab as an adjuvant therapy in
      clinical stage IIIc / IV (no evidence of disease, AJCC (American Joint Committee on Cancer)
      2002) melanoma patients is safe and prolongs overall survival and disease-free interval.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
